description: This version of the  Selfie emoji has the  Medium-dark Skin Tone applied, which is displayed as a Dark Brown Skin Tone on supported plat
apple_vendor_description: The selfie emoji with a medium-dark skin tone, as seen on Apple devices, captures a moment of personal expression with a joyful, confident smile and bright, engaging eyes. The person's face is framed by subtly styled hair, illuminated by soft, natural light that highlights the contours of their features, a hallmark of Apple's realistic 3D shading. This emoji, with its warm undertones and dynamic pose on Apple devices, is frequently used to share personal updates, showcase confidence, or indicate that one is taking a photograph of themselves.
